title: #92Noon! Slogans/Florio/Cardinal/Gorg/JonnyAthletic
description: #92Noon is trying to find the next great Super Bowl Slogan now that "Mission: Minneapolis" is no longer applicable. We also do a "Champions Check" on Gopher hockey/Wolves/Wild to see how our Spring is looking. Ryan Cardinal, Kevin Gorg, and Jon Krawczynski all join, in addition to Florio's weekly spot.
